                    "ref_id": null
                }
            ],
            "ref_spans": [],
            "section": "J o u r n a l P r e -p r o o f"
        },
        {
            "text": "The lock-downs have also changed academic life, with many having to grapple with teaching and assessing on-line. Some have found refereeing and writing away from the office difficult, while others, perhaps with lessened administrative loads have found more time to read, write and referee. However, everyone has been obliged to reflect on the crisis and doubtless such reflection will lead to novel intellectual output on city and environment interactions.",
            "cite_spans": [],
            "ref_spans": [],
            "section": "J o u r n a l P r e -p r o o f"
